<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>280</hymn_number>
<author>mạhr fạyz, mạhr fạyz</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (ʿmry mạ dqt sʿạdẗ fy qlby .. wlạ ḥsyt bslạm fy ḥyạty
 ạ̹lạ fy qrbk ạ̹nt yạ rby .. bạnsy̱ ậlạmy wạḥtyạjạty)2
 ạlqrạr- (mạsẖy fy ạlbryẗ mʿạyạ .. mạsẖy wsạnd ạ̹ydy ʿlyk
 wạsmʿ wʿdk ạ̹frḥ byã .. wlạzm ytẖbt frḥy fyk)2
 2- (ṭwl mạ ʿynyã lyk mrfwʿẗ .. yfḍl qlby byk mrfwʿ
 wạtʿb lmạ bạḥwl ʿyny .. ʿnk wạbqy̱ fy fqr wjwʿ)2
 3- (mhmạ ykwn ạlḥzn fy qlby .. mhmạ ạ̉ʿdy fy ḍʿf wḍyq
 rby ạ̉nạ dạymaⁿạ byk mrfwʿ .. fwq ạlṣʿb mʿạyạ ṣdyq)2</lyrics>
<title>ʿmry mạ dqt sʿạdẗ</title>
</song>